🌿 Genetic Fusion: A Masterpiece Blend of our Cherry Pie Strain, Cannacotta Strain and Purple Punch Strain.

⏰ Harvest Time: A Swift 8-9 Weeks

Description:

Savour the unforgettable and prepare to embark on a taste adventure like no other with Tastebudz Cherry Cheesecake Strain Auto Flowering Feminized Seeds. Crafted from the delectable fusion of Cherry Pie Strain, Cannacotta Strain, and the legendary Purple Punch Auto, this seed brings the essence of a tangy and creamy cherry dessert to your garden, part of the Tastebudz Seeds Auto Mix pack.

 

Indulgence Meets Efficiency:

This astonishing 70% Indica marvel of autoflowering cannabis seeds delivers an intense, enduring effect that initially soars and gently transforms into a sublime body sensation. With a rapid flowering time of just 8-9 weeks, this beauty yields up to 650 g/m² of gourmet cannabis seeds indoors. And when grown outdoors, expect a bountiful harvest of up to 130 g/plant.

 

Elevate Your Senses With Our Cherry Cheesecake Strain:

With an impressive THC content of 25%, these seeds promise to take your senses on a thrilling journey. Dive into a symphony of terpenes, including Beta Caryophyllene, Alpha Humulene, Limonene, Myrcene, Linalool, Nerolidol, Beta Pinene, Geranyl Acetate, Alpha Pinene, Eucalyptol, Alpha Phellendrene, Caryophyllene Oxide, D-3-Carene, and Terpinolene.

 

Variety Awaits:

Tastebudz Cherry Cheesecake Strain Autoflowering Seeds are part of the Tastebudz Syndicate Autoflowering Mix pack, a treasure trove for those seeking a diverse collection of high-quality feminized cannabis seeds to elevate their cannabis seed collection.

 

Cherry Cheesecake Strain A World of Delight at Your Fingertips:

Please note that Tastebudz Syndicate seeds are sold solely as souvenirs in compliance with U.K. laws. But the good news is, these sensational seeds are available from seedbanks worldwide. Discover your nearest distributor now and embark on a journey that celebrates the perfect fusion of taste, aroma, and potency.

Don’t miss the chance to elevate your cannabis cultivation to a realm of unforgettable flavours and sensations.
